{"tid":1362329,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"全民帶長遮運動，救人救己要有一遮。","createTime":"2019-07-25T00:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T00:44:57.000Z","uid":111004,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"73ff399207f20044f318125e0b11cf5800f53ca1","tid":1362329,"uid":111004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:12:49.000Z","msg":"經過721一役，已經證明警方無能力再保護市民。<br />\n避免再次出現「白衣人」襲擊市民個案<br />\n即日起<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔理落雨唔落雨，每日長遮保平安</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ADzKqK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ADzKqK.png&h=a47c22a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長遮作用<br />\n1，遮風擋雨<br />\n2，拉開距離，減少攻擊傷害<br />\n3，遮擋重要部位，避免對方使用腐蝕性或刺激性化學物品<br />\n4，追捕罪犯，善用勾位。就算唔係賽跑冠軍都可以輕易阻止逃犯離開<br />\n5，自衛武器，近攻總比赤手空拳好<br />\n*帶遮出街絕對合法（相比起對方水喉木棍）<br />\n<br />\n全民帶長遮運動除左保護自己外<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">更想表達對政府同警方既不信任</span><br />\n<br />\n如果真係成功，各國媒體將會免費再宣揚香港運動俾世界關注。<br />\n所以希望大家可以廣傳俾身邊朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d21ef4607589ceaf948bd1511269746bec66b27","tid":1362329,"uid":140709,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:17:43.000Z","msg":"推一推<br />\n<br />\nBy落雨一直唔記得帶遮嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日帶就唔洗怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9786a9555034ec539f8c942d68fe53cbb644d103","tid":1362329,"uid":111004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d21ef4607589ceaf948bd1511269746bec66b27","tid":1362329,"uid":140709,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:17:43.000Z","msg":"推一推<br />\n<br />\nBy落雨一直唔記得帶遮嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日帶就唔洗怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:18:24.000Z","msg":"要養成好習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":